      </div>

      <div class="talk">
        <div class="talk-year">2024</div>
        <div>
          <span class="talk-type talk">Talk</span>
          <div class="talk-title">API Security</div>
          <div class="talk-venue">Women Techmakers · International Women's Day 2024</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="cta-band">
        <h3>Want me on your stage?</h3>
        <p>I love conferences, workshops, and community events, especially ones focused on backend engineering, fintech, or women in tech. I travel well. I prepare thoroughly. I will almost certainly over-rehearse.</p>
        <a class="cta-btn" href="mailto:koyejomotunrayo@gmail.com?subject=Speaking%20invitation">Invite me to speak</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>